HEADWORD: Liguliflorous
<hw>Lig`u*li*flo"rous</hw>
<pr>(l⟦icr⟧g`⟦usl⟧*l⟦icr⟧*fl⟦omac⟧"r⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
